### ============================================
### NEXTALX ASSIGNMENT FLOW TEST
### ============================================


### 1) Mevcut çalışanları listele
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/employees?page=0&size=100

###

### 2) Mevcut kategorileri listele
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/categories?page=0&size=100

###

### 3) Asset oluştur
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/assets
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "assetTag": "LT-001",
  "name": "MacBook Pro 16",
  "brand": "Apple",
  "model": "M4 Pro",
  "serialNumber": "APL-2026-001",
  "purchaseDate": "2026-01-01",
  "warrantyEndDate": "2029-01-01",
  "purchasePrice": 125000,
  "supplier": "Apple Türkiye",
  "categoryId": 1
}

###

### 4) Asset listesini kontrol et
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/assets?page=0&size=100

###

### 5) Asset'i çalışana ata
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/assignments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "employeeId": 1,
  "assetId": 1,
  "assignedDate": "2026-07-05",
  "note": "Senior Backend Developer laptop assignment"
}

###

### 6) Assignment listesini getir
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/assignments?page=0&size=100

###

### 7) Asset durumunun ASSIGNED olduğunu doğrula
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/assets?page=0&size=100

###

### 8) Asset'i geri teslim al
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/assignments/1/return

###

### 9) Assignment listesini tekrar kontrol et
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/assignments?page=0&size=100

###

### 10) Asset tekrar AVAILABLE oldu mu kontrol et
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/assets?page=0&size=100

###